This is a special patch file. When this file is read during build,
the following script ensures the -G flag is removed from any compiler flags.
This script is executed as part of the build process:

#!/bin/bash
for xcconfig in $(find "${PODS_ROOT}" -name "*.xcconfig"); do
  if grep -q "\-G" "$xcconfig"; then
